Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.87,0:00:04.90,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,什么嘛 你想干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.87,0:00:10.77,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,由希奈就拜托给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:13.85,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,你这家伙 在说些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:17.22,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,我认为你对她的感情也不假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.97,0:00:19.07,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,所以就把她托付给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:20.75,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,托付什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:23.60,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,请你一定要让由希奈幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:27.22,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,你这家伙 不要自说自话好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.45,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,你觉得由希奈会答应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:30.87,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:33.02,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,擅自就一意孤行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:39.15,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:50.62,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,早呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:53.95,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,索菲 你怎么啦 看你没精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:56.97,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,我在考虑是不是该回法国了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:59.97,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,哎哟 这就是传说中的燃尽症候群吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs45}燃尽症候群：贯彻某种一生都想实现的目标的人最终目标却没有实现时的无力感与疲劳感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:01.75,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,有可能是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:04.97,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,我可能不需要搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:08.02,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,你之前要搬家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:11.12,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,我说过了啊 没有一个人记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:12.95,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,你说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.07,0:01:14.32,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,我说过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:16.60,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,你们看过我的视频了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:19.42,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,最终的部分里我可是有留言的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:21.15,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,我没看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:25.05,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.17,0:01:26.07,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,早哟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:29.17,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,哎呀 感觉由希奈也没什么精神哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.87,0:01:30.75,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我也…？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:33.12,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,索菲也说考虑要不要回法国
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:35.72,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,索菲也要走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:40.42,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,怎么啦 一副世界末日要来了的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.07,0:01:42.07,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,话说 剑酱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:46.82,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,喂 出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:48.07,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,能跟我讲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:50.75,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,他跟我说 永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:53.46,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,哈？ 怎么还有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:55.72,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,到底是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:01:59.95,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,这件事和努也特还有泽鲁有关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:05.22,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,好像最近 提交面见泽鲁的申请也不个许可
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.17,0:02:09.15,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,应该从艾菲德尔克的母舰上得到什么情报了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.95,0:02:13.47,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,从泽鲁先生的母星传来信息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:17.37,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,说马上就要展开与艾菲德尔克的最终决战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:20.42,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,也就是说剑也要去参战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:23.02,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,他们要将虫洞打开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:27.07,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,这是要直指敌人老巢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.32,0:02:28.25,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,能打得赢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:31.05,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,他到底是有多武士道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 还要继续打仗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,会不会有事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不会再被进攻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,再被进攻可遭不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:40.47,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,你们不要再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:42.40,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,那家伙虽然是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:45.00,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,但他并不只考虑自己的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:48.87,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,被救的事 还有泽鲁帮助他的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:50.65,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,他想报答他们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:53.87,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,好不容易赢了 还要接着打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:55.80,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,你怎么不拦着他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:57.80,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,你觉得我能拦得住他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:02:59.95,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,能拦得住就不是剑之介了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:02.15,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,他说过的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:05.52,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,能做那种傻事是很了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:10.05,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,他一定是为了我们才去战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:13.42,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,他就是那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,0:03:20.32,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,白羽 你自己怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:24.70,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,你就放他自己去 也没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:30.90,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,他也很需要你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:38.17,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,嗯 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:41.65,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我要跟剑之介一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.12,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,搞不好你可是会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:47.12,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,剑之介会拼死保护我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:49.12,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,剑酱也可能会死的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:51.62,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我也会拼死保护他的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:54.80,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,这两情相悦是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:57.22,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,但是警卫应该很严的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:04:00.20,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,我会拼死把他们送过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:04.15,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,你要干了这种事 可就进不了国防大学了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:07.30,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,我不会对自己的心情说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:10.17,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,真拿你们没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.80,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,那就帮由希奈私奔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,私奔？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:16.95,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,突然就要侵入艾菲德尔克的飞船里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:18.60,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,这怎么能不去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.02,0:04:21.00,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:27.72,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,可能再也回不来这个世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:29.55,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,你做好觉悟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:35.67,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,或许安稳生活的未来再也不会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:39.90,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,但还有希望 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:44.10,Default,Nouet,0,0,0,,要上路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:46.42,Default,Nouet,0,0,0,,但是真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:49.60,Default,Nouet,0,0,0,,你本来也是这颗星球上的住民
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:53.12,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,在不远的将来 我也会被夺取自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:55.97,Default,Nouet,0,0,0,,但是 由希奈又该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:00.40,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,我不能带她去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:03.62,Default,Nouet,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:08.72,Default,Nouet,0,0,0,,我就将我的性命托付于你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:14.40,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,为什么只有我被没收摄影器械啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.27,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,能放我们进来就不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:19.65,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,老实说 他们肯定很想逮捕我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:23.67,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,问题在于 完全没有足够到逮捕我们的罪名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.35,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,这是问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:29.55,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,话说 茅原的爸爸也在这工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:30.55,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,姑且是咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:34.10,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,呀吼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:36.27,Default,Hausen,0,0,0,,噢噢 纯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:37.75,Default,Hausen,0,0,0,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:38.95,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,我好得很啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:40.20,Default,Hausen,0,0,0,,那就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:42.27,Default,Hausen,0,0,0,,妈妈也不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:45.22,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,好过头了 基本都不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:47.55,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,现在在跟第四任老公在旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:52.80,Default,Hausen,0,0,0,,只要她能幸福 我引身退出也算有价值
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:57.62,Default,Hausen,0,0,0,,我在这里忍受寂寞 潜心投入研究
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:59.67,Default,Hausen,0,0,0,,实在是…嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:01.27,Default,Hausen,0,0,0,,阿咧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:57.65,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,{\an8}爸爸 我借相机用下咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:06.85,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,豪森医生是茅原的爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:07.70,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:10.15,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,父母离异 所以姓也不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:15.02,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,以我的权限虽然无法知道准确情报
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:17.67,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,情报都被不完全保密起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.07,0:06:20.82,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,有什么情报是不想公开的 一目了然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.97,0:06:27.07,Default,Graham,0,0,0,,今天不是定期会面的日子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:27.93,Default,Beth,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,另一个驾驶员是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:34.42,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,竟然监禁保护地球的大英雄 到底怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:35.25,Default,Graham,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:37.25,Default,Beth,0,0,0,,莫非是情报泄漏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:38.47,Default,Graham,0,0,0,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:41.20,Default,Graham,0,0,0,,就是因为不完全保密才会惹麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.27,0:06:43.47,Default,Graham,0,0,0,,不管发生什么都不要开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.17,Default,Graham,0,0,0,,大家可都是人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:48.42,Default,Beth,0,0,0,,本研究所尚处于危险状态
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:50.77,Default,Beth,0,0,0,,请等待正式的发布会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}给我们说清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这所研究所的原则不是一切都公开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:57.80,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,你们打算无视联合国的基本人权路线吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:00.55,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,该差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:03.50,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,不过啊 你还挺能行的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:07.75,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,大人们会编出个什么故事来 我也想过的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:11.65,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,然后我就想 我们这边也编出个故事不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:13.77,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,你要把这个拍成电影吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:15.27,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,我还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:17.65,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,不过 看起来对方已经准备开始避嫌了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:19.70,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,现在这个时机 机不可失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:24.05,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,青马的战斗一定要传递给大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:28.10,Default,Carlos,0,0,0,,单是放给大家看 大家也应该会懂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:31.87,Default,Nouet,0,0,0,,弗朗格尔在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:33.47,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,马没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.12,Default,Zeru,0,0,0,,应该是被挪到更深层的地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:37.27,Default,Zeru,0,0,0,,我心里有数了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:40.47,Default,Zeru,0,0,0,,但是这并不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:50.20,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,是由希奈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:51.35,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:52.17,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:55.35,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,这是第一次跟你打电话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:57.37,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,这么说还真是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:02.80,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,你这家伙 不久之前还惊叹盒子竟然会说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:07.37,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,士别三日当刮目相待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.52,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,那句词是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:11.82,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,你的确不会懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:15.37,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我说 之后你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:18.12,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,不会牵扯到你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:22.12,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,不要说这么令人伤心的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:26.80,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,带上泽鲁和努也特两人离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:28.17,Default,Zeru,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:31.20,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,你这样做太危险了 暂时给我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:32.35,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,不 我不等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:35.95,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,那就别吧手机关掉 知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:39.07,Default,Zeru,0,0,0,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:41.97,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:50.65,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,你自己能掰开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:54.20,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,之前不做是因为我要表示诚意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:58.72,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,这片区域的监控摄像头被毁掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:06.10,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,白羽 你就把我忘掉 然后过上幸福生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:09.45,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我知道了 赤城你可千万别勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:21.52,Default,Akagi,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:29.15,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,大小姐 今日又有何贵干
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:32.72,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,我要为我们的未来战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:38.07,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,如果这就是大小姐的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:41.80,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,我也加入进去吧 为了你的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:43.12,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:48.57,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,那个 茂住先生没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:49.80,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:53.32,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,为了守护未来而奔赴战场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:56.42,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,作为自卫官没有比这更幸福的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:58.80,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,只要别送死就行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:02.92,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,自卫官茂住敏幸将在这里牺牲了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:06.90,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,只要大小姐一声令下 就算是下地狱我也定奉陪到底
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:08.17,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,你还是一个人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:14.40,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,那么 从第一层到最深层的警备系统都失效了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:18.17,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,除了有人亲眼看到以外都不会发现我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:21.17,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,这么简单就能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:26.37,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,跟艾菲德尔克交战的时候我掺入了很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:28.87,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,果然你是做信息战的专家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:33.75,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,那么接下来的问题就是分散在四处的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.07,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,请启动这架机器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:39.57,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.85,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,这是之前在战斗中牺牲的战士的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:45.97,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,你要用「幽灵战术」了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:48.15,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,战场上经常出现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:49.22,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,幽灵…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:51.97,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,接下来如果你搞不好就会被击中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:53.45,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,还是请回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:54.37,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:56.90,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,之前都是侥幸才存活下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:11:00.72,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,把资料保存好然后再编点儿假新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:02.60,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,也能赚到些点击量的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:05.70,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,那还真不是我的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:07.67,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,我可从不会传播谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:10.70,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,公布出去的只会是真相
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:13.90,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,我还真是小瞧你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:14.95,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:19.45,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,有这种觉悟的话 就坚持吧真相放送到底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:33.17,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,连个守卫都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:34.97,Default,Zeru,0,0,0,,很让人在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.07,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,但绝不能在这里停留
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:47.55,Default,Carrie,0,0,0,,青马剑之介时贞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:52.67,Default,Carrie,0,0,0,,你用自己的行为证明自己是个危险分子了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:55.42,Default,Carrie,0,0,0,,放弃逃跑接受逮捕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:03.70,Default,Graham,0,0,0,,哪里着火了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:06.52,Default,Beth,0,0,0,,是被废弃的08区
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:11.37,Default,Beth,0,0,0,,倾斜式电梯区域传来美军部队的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:14.25,Default,Beth,0,0,0,,正在跟身份不明的机器人作战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:14.97,Default,Graham,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有谁出来解释一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:25.17,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,请履行信息公开的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那个机体是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那个不是黑骸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}快拍快拍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:32.80,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,艾菲德尔克的机体走出来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:35.00,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,那个是…黑骸！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:37.67,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,里面究竟发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:40.42,Default,Graham,0,0,0,,是谁在驾驶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:43.10,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我说你为啥跟过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:45.57,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,不播这个播什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:48.04,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,我们有可能回不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:51.12,Default,Kaya,0,0,0,,真假？ 那我就在那边直播好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:53.52,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,这家伙没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:56.10,Default,Beth,0,0,0,,我们要干扰信号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:59.42,Default,Graham,0,0,0,,你现在进行信息管制 只是在火上浇油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:01.42,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,你在发什么火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:04.70,Default,Graham,0,0,0,,所长…是前所长 为什么在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:07.45,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,卸任的准备工作太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:10.40,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,先不说这个 警备系统已经挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:13.02,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,形同虚设啊 这里的警备系统
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:15.00,Default,Graham,0,0,0,,你就不要给我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:19.20,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,你现在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:20.10,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,在走廊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:21.37,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,在哪个走廊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:24.80,Default,Zeru,0,0,0,,真是了不起的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:27.15,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,你现在在直播吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:30.47,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,我在你正面对着的大楼右边一层
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:31.55,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:37.72,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,黑骸！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:46.07,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,泽鲁 带我一起走 我也要战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:47.57,Default,Zeru,0,0,0,,这不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:51.65,Default,Zeru,0,0,0,,我们就是为了不让你们卷进来才决定自己走的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:54.82,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,我知道 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:57.87,Default,Zeru,0,0,0,,再会了 很感谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:02.45,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,祝武运昌隆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:08.82,Default,Carrie,0,0,0,,快阻止黑骸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:10.22,Default,Graham,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:12.55,Default,Hausen,0,0,0,,让黑骸跟美杜莎停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:17.37,Default,Tom,0,0,0,,好的 得好好爆一下这些小混蛋们的菊花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:28.57,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,诶 泽鲁先生 为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:30.45,Default,Paula,0,0,0,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:33.32,Default,Zeru,0,0,0,,枢石处于不稳定状态 很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:34.90,Default,Paula,0,0,0,,来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.15,0:14:39.10,Default,Paula,0,0,0,,不稳定状态是怎么一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:40.77,Default,Zeru,0,0,0,,这交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:46.55,Default,Paula,0,0,0,,次郎 先让大家去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:51.32,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,好的 大家快去避难 快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.12,Default,Paula,0,0,0,,你是要启动枢石？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:54.60,Default,Zeru,0,0,0,,对不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.05,Default,Paula,0,0,0,,该道歉的是我们才对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:15:00.37,Default,Paula,0,0,0,,非常感谢你对人类做的贡献
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:01.57,Default,Paula,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:06.70,Default,Zeru,0,0,0,,有像你一样的人在 我的努力就没白搭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:08.37,Default,Paula,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:15.60,Default,Zeru,0,0,0,,因为紧急启动和中止 枢石受到巨大的损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:18.77,Default,Zeru,0,0,0,,现在再启动一次可能就会崩坏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:20.45,Default,Paula,0,0,0,,会造成灾害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:23.05,Default,Zeru,0,0,0,,崩坏的同时就会销毁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.72,0:15:26.62,Default,Zeru,0,0,0,,它就拜托给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:29.77,Default,Zeru,0,0,0,,只要它在飞船的解析就能一直进行下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.25,0:15:30.50,Default,Paula,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:47.02,Default,Zeru,0,0,0,,680秒后枢石就会启动
