Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:08.42,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:10.97,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,未来战场上你会遭不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:13.60,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,不试一下怎么会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:15.92,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,不行 去了就回不来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:19.45,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,你能活着回来都是多亏了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:22.52,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,要是没有我 你一下就会死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.57,0:16:27.37,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,这点我承认 不愧是我的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:30.17,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,明明现在还不是你妻子！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:33.95,Default,Mika,0,0,0,,打情骂俏对着全世界直播了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:39.82,Default,Nouet,0,0,0,,看你们这样 百看不厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:41.32,Default,Nouet,0,0,0,,这不是很好么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:44.80,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,好吧 我带你去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:46.25,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,跟上 由希奈
