Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:16:57.27,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:16:59.55,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,你在干什么 快下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:03.07,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,妈 我要和剑之介一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:04.60,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,哈？ 当真？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:05.40,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:11.12,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,那你自己决心 一定要贯彻到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:14.00,Default,Hiromi,0,0,0,,但是正要一定要回来
